name: EMODnet Physics Data Catalog
description: The EMODnet Physics catalog gathers oceanographic data for public dissemination, integrating data from European and global marine infrastructures, including platforms such as EuroGOOS, Copernicus Marine Service, SeaDataNet, ICES, PANGAEA, and more. It provides comprehensive in-situ ocean physics data, supporting machine-to-machine interaction and offering datasets in various formats.
owner_name: European Marine Observation and Data Network (EMODnet)
